1821
02:26:33.310 --> 02:26:34.250
<i>You'll figure it out.</i>

1822
02:26:36.110 --> 02:26:39.830
<i>This is Dr. Captain Ryland Grace
reporting from the Hail Mary.</i>

1823
02:26:39.970 --> 02:26:41.970
<i>As the Eridians say...</i>

1824
02:26:58.970 --> 02:26:59.950
Let's begin.

1825
02:27:52.550 --> 02:27:53.890
Good morning. Armando.

1826
02:27:55.370 --> 02:27:56.410
You shouldn't have.

1827
02:28:02.130 --> 02:28:03.190
That's a noogie.

1828
02:28:03.610 --> 02:28:05.130
I'm coming!

1829
02:28:12.130 --> 02:28:14.220
Why you take so long?

1830
02:28:14.330 --> 02:28:15.390
Why you always
gotta be so early?

1831
02:28:15.400 --> 02:28:17.400
I knock and I knock.

1832
02:28:17.490 --> 02:28:20.050
Yeah. I know. and I ignored you.

1833
02:28:20.290 --> 02:28:21.170
- Grace. the door.
- Oh.

1834
02:28:21.190 --> 02:28:23.190
- Close the door.
- Yeah.

1835
02:28:24.050 --> 02:28:26.610
Why? I thought this
was a safe neighborhood.

1836
02:28:26.650 --> 02:28:28.230
I make door. You close door.

1837
02:28:28.230 --> 02:28:28.800
Okay.

1838
02:28:28.820 --> 02:28:30.850
It's just Armando likes the fresh air.

1839
02:28:44.570 --> 02:28:46.970
Can we talk about the water
temperature a little bit?

1840
02:28:46.980 --> 02:28:48.070
Yes.

1841
02:28:48.090 --> 02:28:48.950
It's amazing.

1842
02:28:48.970 --> 02:28:51.110
Just that you've done it at all.

1843
02:28:52.330 --> 02:28:53.050
Very cold.

1844
02:28:53.970 --> 02:28:55.730
And. before. it was boiling.

1845
02:28:56.510 --> 02:28:57.390
Is there an in-between?

1846
02:28:58.510 --> 02:28:59.840
I ask Adrian to work on this.

1847
02:29:06.310 --> 02:29:11.090
Please tell the bio-dome
illumination team that it's perfect now.

1848
02:29:11.760 --> 02:29:14.260
You no want it sunnier than this?

1849
02:29:14.290 --> 02:29:18.050
Oh no. this is. you know
I'm a sucker for the fog.

1850
02:29:27.130 --> 02:29:28.220
Grace.

1851
02:29:28.250 --> 02:29:29.650
Yeah. pal.

1852
02:29:30.470 --> 02:29:33.220
Eridian scientists are ready...

1853
02:29:33.260 --> 02:29:35.510
to prepare Hail Mary for journey home.

1854
02:29:43.550 --> 02:29:44.770
Can I think about it?

1855
02:29:46.470 --> 02:29:48.800
Yes. think about it long time.

1856
02:30:35.410 --> 02:30:37.850
Good morning. class.

1857
02:30:39.030 --> 02:30:39.830
Okay.

1858
02:30:39.860 --> 02:30:42.390
Everyone. take their seats.

1859
02:30:43.430 --> 02:30:44.710
Let's wake up.

1860
02:30:48.610 --> 02:30:50.150
Who can tell me
the speed of light?

